[size=3]Based on the original [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/11]Anti-Inflation Mod[/url] and [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/graveyardkeeper/mods/17]Anti-Inflation Mod Reverse - Remove Sell Deflation[/url] mods. All credit for the original ideas and implementations goes to their authors.[/size]

